m_q.target_metric: Player with highest number of titles
sub_questions: What is the maximum value in 'No. of Titles' column?
Which player(s) have this maximum number of titles?

format_notes: All numeric columns are Int64 type
No missing values observed in sample

constraints: No. of Titles must be non-negative integer
Rank should be unique or tied
Final Appearances should be >= No. of Titles + Runner-up
output_format_requirements: Return player name(s) with highest No. of Titles
Include the number of titles in output
